WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
Welcome to today's championship match between the Eagles and the Hawks!

00:00:03.500 --> 00:00:07.200
The Eagles are looking strong in the first quarter with their aggressive offense.

00:00:07.200 --> 00:00:11.800
Johnson takes the shot from the three-point line... and it's good! Eagles lead 15-12.

00:00:11.800 --> 00:00:15.400
The Hawks are responding well with their defensive strategy.

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:19.100
Smith drives to the basket, avoids the block, and scores! What a play!

00:00:19.100 --> 00:00:23.600
Timeout called by the Eagles coach. They need to regroup after that last possession.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:27.300
The crowd is electric tonight! Over 15,000 fans in attendance.

00:00:27.300 --> 00:00:31.000
Back from the timeout, the Eagles inbound the ball to Thompson.

00:00:31.000 --> 00:00:34.700
Thompson passes to Williams who's open in the corner...

00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:38.400
Williams shoots! It's off the rim but Davis gets the rebound!

00:00:38.400 --> 00:00:42.100
Davis puts it back up and scores! Eagles extend their lead to 19-14.

00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:45.800
The Hawks are calling for a substitution. Rodriguez coming in for Martinez.

00:00:45.800 --> 00:00:49.500
Rodriguez immediately makes an impact with a steal!

00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:53.200
He's racing down the court on a fast break...

00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:56.900
Rodriguez passes to Brown who's trailing behind...

00:00:56.900 --> 00:01:00.600
Brown takes the shot from mid-range and it's nothing but net!

00:01:00.600 --> 00:01:04.300
Hawks cut the deficit to just 3 points. This game is heating up!

00:01:04.300 --> 00:01:08.000
The Eagles are bringing the ball up court with Thompson at the point.

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:11.700
Thompson calls for a screen from Davis...

00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:15.400
Davis sets the pick, Thompson uses it perfectly!

00:01:15.400 --> 00:01:19.100
Thompson drives to the basket and draws the foul!

00:01:19.100 --> 00:01:22.800
He'll go to the free throw line for two shots.

00:01:22.800 --> 00:01:26.500
First free throw... it's good! Eagles lead 20-16.

00:01:26.500 --> 00:01:30.200
Second free throw... also good! Eagles up by 6 points.

00:01:30.200 --> 00:01:33.900
The Hawks are pushing the pace now, looking to get back in this game.

00:01:33.900 --> 00:01:37.600
Rodriguez brings the ball up quickly and finds Smith in the post.

00:01:37.600 --> 00:01:41.300
Smith backs down his defender and goes for the hook shot...

00:01:41.300 --> 00:01:45.000
It's good! Smith with the smooth post move. Hawks trail 22-18.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.700
Just 2 minutes left in the first quarter. Both teams playing excellent basketball.

00:01:48.700 --> 00:01:52.400
The Eagles are looking to extend their lead before the quarter ends.

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:56.100
Williams takes a deep three-pointer... it's off the mark!

00:01:56.100 --> 00:01:59.800
Brown grabs the rebound for the Hawks and starts the fast break.

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:03.500
Brown passes ahead to Rodriguez who's sprinting down the court...

00:02:03.500 --> 00:02:07.200
Rodriguez goes up for the layup and scores! What a beautiful play!

00:02:07.200 --> 00:02:10.900
Hawks are now only down by 2 points with 30 seconds left in the quarter.

00:02:10.900 --> 00:02:14.600
The Eagles are taking their time with this possession.

00:02:14.600 --> 00:02:18.300
Thompson holds the ball at the top of the key, looking for an opening.

00:02:18.300 --> 00:02:22.000
He drives left, draws the defense, and kicks it out to Williams!

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:25.700
Williams shoots the three... it's good! Eagles lead 25-20!

00:02:25.700 --> 00:02:29.400
That's the end of the first quarter. Eagles lead by 5 points.

00:02:29.400 --> 00:02:33.100
What an exciting start to this championship game!

00:02:33.100 --> 00:02:36.800
Both teams are showing why they deserve to be here tonight.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:40.500
We'll be back after a short break with the second quarter action.
